(49, 1697275907, '188.129.156.100', 1, 'Arshan aghaei', 'nope', 'noy85141@gmail.com', 'Hello, I hope you are doing well.\n\nMy name is arshan, im 16 and i live nearby \"vip intellect group\".\nAfter learning and researching about your values, missions and accomplishments, I thought my skills would be useful, so I would like to work there.\n\nI have a c1 mastery of the English language, demonstrating proficiency in both oral and written. I am good at teaching, I have a lot of free time so I have been thinking about getting a job somewhere that my skills would be useful for.\n\nIf there are any open positions that requires my skills. I would be happy to oblige.\n\nSincerely\n\n-Arshan', 'ge', 1, 0),
